Class NotIdentifiableEventImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • jakarta.xml.bind.helpers.ValidationEventImpl
      • jakarta.xml.bind.helpers.NotIdentifiableEventImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    NotIdentifiableEvent, ValidationEvent
    public class NotIdentifiableEventImpl
extends ValidationEventImpl
implements NotIdentifiableEvent
    Default implementation of the NotIdentifiableEvent interface.

    Jakarta XML Binding providers are allowed to use whatever class that implements the ValidationEvent interface. This class is just provided for a convenience.

    Author:
    • Ryan Shoemaker, Sun Microsystems, Inc.
    See Also:
    NotIdentifiableEvent, ValidationEventHandler, ValidationEvent, ValidationEventLocator

        Create a new NotIdentifiableEventImpl.
